snippet: State investigators say there is no evidence that Planned Parenthood in Florida bought or sold human organs or tissue.
abstract: Florida state investigations into Planned Parenthood clinics yield no evidence supporting claims human organs or tissue were bought and sold; Gov Rick Scott ordered inspections following controversial videos in which organization officials discuss fetal organ research.
lead_paragraph: State investigators say there is no evidence that Planned Parenthood in Florida bought or sold human organs or tissue.

headline.main: Florida: State Finds No Evidence Against Planned Parenthood
headline.print_headline: Florida: State Finds No Evidence Against Planned Parenthood
